section.def:
appellant
                (上訴人) means a person who has given notice of
            appeal;

Chairman
                (主席) means the chairman of the Tribunal appointed
            under section 48(1) of the Ordinance;

hearing
                (聆訊) means the hearing of an appeal and includes
            a preliminary hearing;

Secretary
                (秘書) means the Secretary to the Appeal Tribunal
            appointed under section 46 of the Ordinance;
